  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/fskit\/fsvolume\/openmodes\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T15:49:49Z\n---\n\n# FSVolume.OpenModes\n\n**Structure**\n\nDefined modes for opening a file.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstruct OpenModes\n```\n\n## Declaring open modes\n\n- **read**: The read mode.\n- **write**: The write mode.\n\n## Working with raw values\n\n- **init(rawValue:)**\n\n## Opening and closing\n\n- **openItem(_:modes:replyHandler:)**: Opens a file for access.\n- **closeItem(_:modes:replyHandler:)**: Closes a file from further access.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- BitwiseCopyable\n- Equatable\n- ExpressibleByArrayLiteral\n- OptionSet\n- RawRepresentable\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n- SetAlgebra\n\n",
